<SAGPLayout title="Annual Conference 2024 | SAGP">

<PageHero
  kicker="Annual Conference 2024"
  title="Pre-Socratics, Plato, Aristotle, and the Stoics."
  subtitle="November 16–17, 2024 · via Zoom · All times listed in Pacific Standard Time."
  image="/assets/images/parthenon_night.jpg"
/>

<section class="section two-col">
  <div>
    <h2>About the 2024 conference</h2>
  </div>

  <div>
    <p>
      The 2024 Annual Conference explored four major areas of Ancient Greek
      philosophy through themed panel discussions bringing together scholars
      from universities around the world.
    </p>

    <p>
      To attend via Zoom, contact
      <a href="mailto:apreus@binghamton.edu">apreus@binghamton.edu</a>,
      indicating which session or sessions you wish to attend.
    </p>

    <div class="callout">
      All times are Pacific Standard Time. Time-zone conversion charts should
      be included here for international participants.
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

